textBeforeTable: Rapala Jointed Lure Specifications: Bass, Walleye, Pike, Musky, Trout, Salmon, Panfish, Redfish, Tarpon, Snook, Tuna, Sea Trout, Striper, Grouper, Peacock Bass, Kingfish, Bluefish, Wahoo, Dolphin Rapala Jointed Lure Species: Hand Tuned & Tank Tested Works Top To Bottom Classic Minnow Profile Broken Back Design Rapala Jointed Lure Features: These lures are great for casting or trolling in freshwater or saltwater. They have a running depth between 3 and 14 feet. With its slight exaggeration of Rapala's unique baitfish-in-distress behavior, the Jointed™ gets the undivided attention of otherwise uninterested gamefish. This articulated, or "broken back" lure can be fished like the Original Floater®, top to bottom. It is the perfect choice after a cold front, when fish are traditionally finicky and in a negative feeding mood.
